Privacy Policy for Taobao Image Downloader & Assistant
Last Updated: March 4, 2026

This Privacy Policy describes how our Chrome Extension ("the Extension") handles user data. We are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring transparency regarding the data we access.

1. Scope of Data Access
The Extension is designed strictly for e-commerce productivity. Our code is configured to only operate on the following authorized domains:

*.taobao.com

*.tmall.com

*.1688.com

*.alibaba.com

We DO NOT collect, store, or transmit your browsing history, personal communications, or data from any websites outside of these specified e-commerce platforms.

2. Information Collection and Usage
To provide the features described in our store listing, we access the following information:

Product Media: We access product images and videos on supported pages to facilitate one-click downloads.

Image Search Data: When you use the "Search by Image" feature, the selected image is temporarily processed to find matching products across the web. This data is not stored permanently.

Translation Content: When you trigger the "Webpage Translation" or "Screenshot Translation" features, text content is processed solely to provide the translated output.

Cookies: We use the cookies permission strictly to maintain your login session on the supported shopping sites to ensure features like "Export Cart" function correctly.

3. Permissions Justification
activeTab & Scripting: Required to interact with the current shopping page for image extraction.

ContextMenus: Required to provide right-click shortcuts for "Search by Image" and "Translation".

DeclarativeNetRequest: Used solely to optimize network requests and improve the loading speed of product images.

4. Data Sharing and Disclosure
No Third-Party Sale: We never sell, rent, or trade your data to third-party advertisers or data brokers.

Data Encryption: All data transmitted for search or translation features is encrypted via HTTPS.

